The Vienna Regional Directorate of Public Health and the Medical Crisis Staff of the City of Vienna provide regular updates about the current case numbers and other figures about the Covid-19 virus. As of Sunday July 26, 2020, 8:00 am, 4,840 (+60) positive tests have been confirmed in Vienna.
